                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="14459712" author="jstrachan" created="Thu, 30 Oct 2003 06:44:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We basically need to put all the import stuff into the AST inside a ModuleNode in the AST.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Then before we generate the bytecode we can iterate through all the AST class nodes adding their names to a set. Then when we verify a ClassNode prior to generating the bytecode we can then check for variables which are class names in the AST (and not yet bytecode generated) or check for names on the classpath.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14459640" author="jstrachan" created="Fri, 31 Oct 2003 03:05:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed. We now have a CompileUnit with all the AST nodes before we generate bytecode so we can do all the necessary class name checks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
